                     <interp inst="t18440610-1596-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing one handkerchief, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18440610-name-433" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18440610-name-433" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
